name: An exploration of info-overload (wdduskchnet level 03) [2009]
description:
An exploration suggested by Derren Brown’s work in the area of human responses to information overload. Due to the high-bandwidth nature of the imagery it is possible that what appears on your screen will be affected by factors including your device, your connection, the overall network, etc.

640 x 480 MP4, H.264 codec, 29.97fps, NTSC gamut, duration 1 minute 14 seconds. Original abstract electronic soundtrack, 48kHz / 32 bits, stereo.
